Interface SecuredResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FrontsNode, RDFNode, Resource, SecuredItem, SecuredRDFNode
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SecuredAlt, SecuredBag, SecuredContainer, SecuredProperty, SecuredRDFList, SecuredReifiedStatement, SecuredSeq
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SecuredAltImpl, SecuredBagImpl, SecuredContainerImpl, SecuredPropertyImpl, SecuredRDFListImpl, SecuredReifiedStatementImpl, SecuredResourceImpl, SecuredSeqImpl

    public interface SecuredResource
extends Resource, SecuredRDFNode
    The interface for secured Resource instances. Use the SecuredResource.Factory to create instances
